title: Head To Head: SJSU vs. Auburn preview and prediction
text: comments Head To Head: SJSU vs. Auburn preview and prediction Head To Head: San Jose State vs Auburn prediction Annice Deweese (45-15) and Kevin Scarbinsky (39-21) are back with another episode of "Head To Head"! This week, the dynamic duo are prediction what will be the outcome of Auburn's 2015 Homecoming game against SJSU - a game that will be closer than originally thought!
